.TP
\f[B]--cstate-prewake\f[R]
Get current setting for c-state prewake (details in
\[aq]cstate_prewake\[aq]).
.TP
\f[B]--idle-driver\f[R]
Get idle driver (details in \[aq]idle_driver\[aq]).
.TP
\f[B]--governor\f[R]
Get idle governor (details in \[aq]governor\[aq]).
